text: Daphnella eocaenica is an extinct species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Raphitomidae.MNHN, Paris: Daphnella (s. str.) eocaenica Cossmann, 1896 ==Distribution== Fossils of this marine species were found in Eocene strata of Loire-Atlantique, France. ==References== * Cossmann (M.), 1896 Essais de Paléoconchologie comparée (2ème livraison), p. 1-179 * Cossmann (M.), 1896 Mollusques éocèniques de la Loire-Inférieure. Tome 1, fascicule 2. Bulletin de la Société des Sciences Naturelles de l'Ouest de la France, t. 6, vol. 4, p. 180-246 eocaenica Category:Gastropods described in 1896
title: Daphnella eocaenica
